text:
Had dinner here today and the duck portions are so GENEROOOOOOUS! $7.20 for duck noodles or duck rice.
So full!!! Happy tummies for the two of us.

Also, don’t need to queue nor be packed like sardines cos this mall is good for a quiet meal!!
Ordered the three combi duck, roast pork and char siew for $18-19. All barely can pass... Maybe the grilled char siew 3.5/5? Nothing to shout about plus it's pricy.
A very good plate of char siew noodle. The meat is roasted with a good amount of char but not overdone.
